{"tid":2397110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國務卿布林肯與楊潔篪通話 提到美方會捍衛香港 新疆 西藏的人權與民主價值並關切中國威脅台海穩定","createTime":"2021-02-06T07:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T07:35:46.000Z","uid":292499,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"757d1102f53bbd6cabced6df8c4005f28a7b708c","tid":2397110,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T07:07:31.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿布林肯今天與中共中央外事工作委員會辦公室主任楊潔篪首度通話。布林肯說，美方將持續捍衛新疆、西藏與香港的人權及民主價值，也會為威脅台海穩定對中國究責。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n布林肯在電話中強調，美國會持續捍衛包含在新疆、西藏與香港等地的人權與民主價值，也會敦促中國加入國際社會行列，共同譴責緬甸軍事政變。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n兩人通話4天前，楊潔篪才透過美國智庫活動，向拜登政府喊話，呼籲美方尊重美中三公報、恪守「一中原則」，停止干涉涉及中國主權與領土完整的香港、西藏、新疆事務。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102060081.aspx?utm_source=cna.app&amp;utm_medium=app&amp;utm_campaign=inapp_share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202102060081.aspx%3Futm_source%3Dcna.app%26utm_medium%3Dapp%26utm_campaign%3Dinapp_share&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIfUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=ad3926f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102060081.aspx?utm_source=cna.app&amp;utm_medium=app&amp;utm_campaign=inapp_share</a>"},{"pid":"dc9a0d82757c499c8d604a14516cc30b1d8e37f2","tid":2397110,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T07:08:34.000Z","msg":"已經傾好咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實係強調<span class=\"red\">唔會</span>捍衛新疆西藏香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老味<br />\n手法同共和黨爭咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da54130d95023166224d53c72a65f17f8053e43","tid":2397110,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T07:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 